<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>游戏中心</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="title">生存直播挑战</h1>
        
        <div class="trigger-rules">
            <h2>🎡 转盘触发规则</h2>
            <div class="rules-grid">
                <div class="rule-item">
                    <span class="rule-icon">⏰</span>
                    <div class="rule-text">
                        <strong>定时触发：</strong><br>
                        开播时，如果当前转盘小于10次，则每一小时强制增加一次
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="rule-item">
                    <span class="rule-icon">🎁</span>
                    <div class="rule-text">
                        <strong>礼物累计：</strong><br>
                        礼物价值累计到100元触发一次转盘
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="rule-item">
                    <span class="rule-icon">⚓</span>
                    <div class="rule-text">
                        <strong>舰长特权：</strong><br>
                        舰长可指定转盘任务
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="game-grid">
            <a href="/spin" class="game-card">
                <div class="game-icon">🎡</div>
                <h2>Spin</h2>
                <p>挑战任务轮盘</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/quiz" class="game-card">
                <div class="game-icon">🧠</div>
                <h2>Quiz</h2>
                <p>知识挑战积分系统</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/slot" class="game-card">
                <div class="game-icon">🎰</div>
                <h2>Slot</h2>
                <p>金额转动机</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/scratch" class="game-card">
                <div class="game-icon">🎟️</div>
                <h2>Scratch</h2>
                <p>刮奖金额卡</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>